Manchester United and Real Madrid legend David Beckham proved he’s still got it by scoring a cheeky nutmeg goal during an Inter Miami training session. Beckham spent six years in Major League Soccer with LA Galaxy and had an option to purchase an expansion franchise as part of his contract. He decided to exercise that option in 2014 and is now one of the owners of Inter Miami, who made their MLS debut in March 2020. Watch the video here. The post Watch: David Beckham scores filthy nutmeg goal in training appeared first on Football News –. Read the Original Article